These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, punk, classical, electronic
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, indian, french, japanese
City: prague, hannover, colone, hamburg
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, goldfish, dog
 1. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person traveling to prague##8
 2. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
 3. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to prague is not to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##8
 5. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
 6. the french is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 8. the japanese is between the owner of the fish and the person traveling to hannover##2
 9. the owner of the dog is the french##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
11. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the mexican##3
12. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
13. the french is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8
14. the fan of punk is the owner of the goldfish##1
15. the fan of punk is not the person traveling to hannover##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | country     | punk   | electronic | classical |
| Nationality   | indian | japanese   | mexican   | french  |
| City         | hannover  | colone  | hamburg  | prague |
| Pet     | turtle    | goldfish | fish     | dog    |

