.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, british, dutch, french
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain, fonseca, oliveros
House: craftsman, cape-cod, farmhouse, art-deco
4 different games are played: chess, domino, canasta, snooker
 1. the farmhouse house is between the person playing chess and the cape-cod house##2
 2. the british is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 3. the british is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 4. the chinese is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
 5. the person playing chess is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
 6. the oliveros-smoker is not to the right of the french##8
 7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 8. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
 9. the craftsman house is the person playing domino##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
11. the person playing chess is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
12. the french is on the left of the british##1
13. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
14. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
15. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
16. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
17. the chinese is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
18. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
19. the french is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | chinese | dutch | french  | british  |
| Cigar          | oliveros     | cain | chaman | fonseca  |
| House   | cape-cod    | farmhouse  | art-deco | craftsman |
| Game           | canasta | snooker | chess    | domino  |

