.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, mauve, azure, orange
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, lemonade, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, coach, nurse, designer
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, london, liverpool
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 2. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
 3. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
 5. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 6. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 7. the nurse is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the coach##8
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Color         | chestnut    | orange   | azure | mauve |
| Beverage   | fanta     | lemonade  | sprite   | 7up      |
| Job   | coach | doctor    | nurse      | designer       |
| City         | london    | edinburgh | liverpool   | san-francisco    |

