 5. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is the bluemaster-smoker##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
13. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
14. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
