The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, march, august
 1. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person drinking coffee##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the person who likes lilac##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 8. the person who likes brown is the person driving the trike##1
 9. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
10. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
11. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person drinking sprite and the person driving the trike##2
12. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
13. the person who likes brown is not to the right of the person driving the trike##8
14. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
