 4. the fan of dubstep is the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person eating cherry is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person eating papaya##7
 7. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
 8. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes green##7
 9. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of trance is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
11. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
12. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
13. the person playing snooker is the person who likes turquise##1
14. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
15. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
16. the fan of trance is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8

.:: Answer ::.
