 1. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 4. the person drinking tea is the person who likes azure##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 6. the person who likes red is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
 7. the person who likes green is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
11. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
12. the person playing backgammon is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person playing poker##2
13. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3

